{"tid":1396943,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有少少嘢想同做緊警察講","createTime":"2019-08-02T09:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T10:01:21.000Z","uid":6024,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce62d3a3982f725da8ab801201ecaee20841c77","tid":1396943,"uid":6024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:14:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">依家香港已經無新一代睇得你起<br />\n淨返啲過期廢老撐你哋同大陸狗<br />\n其實你哋醜唔醜呢<br />\n日日要諗會唔會俾人起底<br />\n仲要俾自己伙記爆出嚟<br />\n出街敢唔敢話自己做緊警察？<br />\n點解唔辭職又咪為錢講到尾<br />\n你自己諗吓拉過幾多黑社會囉<br />\n依一世你哋只可以做隻過街老鼠<br />\n抬唔起頭做人嘅狗<br />\n只可以同一班所謂志同道合嘅狗友圍爐<br />\n每日都好期待有人爆料<br />\n等人睇到香港警察有幾出色<br />\n可能三萬個都有一個好嘅<br />\n一個咁多囉</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察 正一垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"6cb2737d752eb5bfc0ff6fd13efa98a329076c93","tid":1396943,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:14:56.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"fa3d8ddeca6a688ef3e26dbdfd6989e3d41d620b","tid":1396943,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建議新增觀塘，八區集會</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ecfd6d42f9718e7cdaae4c5808801053c0c811b","tid":1396943,"uid":296789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好仔唔當差，當差正仆街</span></span>"},{"pid":"cee962f84a886239774c5dbb2497e9cc124562ff","tid":1396943,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ecfd6d42f9718e7cdaae4c5808801053c0c811b","tid":1396943,"uid":296789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好仔唔當差，當差正仆街</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:21:58.000Z","msg":"廢老嘅至理名言，但佢地偏偏支持"},{"pid":"f85fe241eedaa4c13ba805351a7049bc08187c43","tid":1396943,